Sea horrors are monsters found in The Shadow Reef.

These monsters attack with very strong melee attacks, and they also possess a special attack where they scream at the player and cause very high soft typeless damage to players within seven spaces of their target. A Witchwood icon can be worn to reduce the damage this attack does.

Unlike other monsters in elite dungeons (with the exception of Kal'gerion demons), sea horrors do not pursue players outside their initial location. Some sea horrors continually respawn.
